{"tid":2161608,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警濫射逾1.6萬催淚彈 兒科權威指無解藥：可損兒童肺功能","createTime":"2020-08-17T15:52:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-18T13:45:10.000Z","uid":240362,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"937c7eba1d37781be37f30ef44d02c363a5a07b0","tid":2161608,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:52:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/7OZTE3EXXBH4RI4LFYB5U2T7TU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2F7OZTE3EXXBH4RI4LFYB5U2T7TU%2F&d=hvnZYtOEdtVTkBm9e3s21BIalbmCHUgENExjn%2BY9RKk%3D&h=0ae181e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200817%2F7OZTE3EXXBH4RI4LFYB5U2T7TU%2F&h=f0e432ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200817/7OZTE3EXXBH4RI4LFYB5U2T7TU/</a><br />\n<br />\n過去一年多，警方濫發逾1.6萬枚催淚彈，惟彈藥成份從未公開，亦不知對人體有多大遺禍。兒科權威專家、兒童醫院深切治療部韓錦倫醫生，在最新一期《香港醫學雜誌》撰文強調，催淚彈可導致最少17種症狀，或對兒童造成深遠禍害，美國兒科醫學會（AAP）已作論證；即使本港未有實際個案，衞生當局也應考慮設立監測計劃，追蹤曾吸入催淚氣體的兒童長期健康發展。"},{"pid":"9a9f221027a6bc7248c8ccecc6a5aa275f866085","tid":2161608,"uid":173599,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:53:49.000Z","msg":"毒殺下一代 清洗人口<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/poison.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d32224a4ce808a6b997c237cd20c29fe9a6fa2","tid":2161608,"uid":34444,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T15:53:50.000Z","msg":"邊個兒科權威咁串<br />\n即刻派速龍小隊拘捕佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/11.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7857bd8319d82c54ade08acab46bf223fd188ef","tid":2161608,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:00:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3440eca3246adb7a4e629ba3fe655ad504cd1d5c","tid":2161608,"uid":11291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T16:02:33.000Z","msg":"咁樣放法<br />\n唔好講人<br />\n<br